    <h2>Shopping Cart Application</h2>
    <p></p>
        
        <p>This application is a JavaScript based Shopping Cart application </p>
        <p><b>Software used:</b> Visual Studio </p>
        <p><b>Language:</b>JavaScript, HTML, CSS, JQuery</p>
        <p><b>Application Break Down:</b> This applicaiton consists of a 'Buy Item' input form that is used by the user to input their 
            purchases, this form interacts with the Shopping table listing, when the submit button is pressed, which is used to list the items in the 
        shopping cart.  The user also has the ability to delete items from the shopping cart.  The website can be closed and re-opened again, in the same browser, and the items will 
        remain.  The item list is stored locally.</p>
